Letter,
26 February 1862,
from Nathaniel Ross, Warwick County, to James Ross (
Crack
), Fluvanna County, concerning his reenlistment and James' possible enlistment. He mentions the capture of Fort Donaldson.

Letter,
21 March 1862,
from Nathaniel Ross, Suffolk, to his brother James Ross (
Crack
), Fluvanna County, concerning reenlistment and the draft.
